### PlaylistSync API — REST Client (requires humao.rest-client extension)
### Run any request with the "Send Request" link that appears above it.

@host = http://localhost:5001
@frontendHost = http://localhost:5173

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Auth
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Check connection status (use after logging in via the browser)
GET {{host}}/auth/status
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1

###

### Kick off Spotify OAuth (opens in browser)
GET {{host}}/auth/spotify/login

###

### Kick off Tidal OAuth (opens in browser)
GET {{host}}/auth/tidal/login

###

### Disconnect Spotify
DELETE {{host}}/auth/spotify
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1

###

### Disconnect Tidal
DELETE {{host}}/auth/tidal
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Playlists
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### List Spotify playlists
GET {{host}}/api/playlists/spotify
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1

###

### List Tidal playlists
GET {{host}}/api/playlists/tidal
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1

###

### Get tracks for a Spotify playlist (replace playlist ID)
GET {{host}}/api/playlists/spotify/37i9dQZF1DXcBWIGoYBM5M/tracks
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1

###

### Get tracks for a Tidal playlist (replace playlist ID)
GET {{host}}/api/playlists/tidal/12345678/tracks
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Sync mappings
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all mappings for the current user
GET {{host}}/api/sync/mappings
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1

###

### Create a new mapping (replace playlist IDs)
POST {{host}}/api/sync/mappings
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceService": "spotify",
  "sourcePlaylistId": "37i9dQZF1DXcBWIGoYBM5M",
  "targetService": "tidal",
  "targetPlaylistId": "12345678",
  "direction": "Bidirectional",
  "autoSync": true
}

###

### Update a mapping (replace mapping ID)
PATCH {{host}}/api/sync/mappings/1
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "autoSync": false,
  "direction": "SourceToTarget"
}

###

### Delete a mapping (replace mapping ID)
DELETE {{host}}/api/sync/mappings/1
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Sync operations
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Trigger a manual sync (replace mapping ID)
POST {{host}}/api/sync/mappings/1/sync
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1

###

### Get per-track sync status for a mapping (replace mapping ID)
GET {{host}}/api/sync/mappings/1/status
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1

###

### View sync logs (optional ?mappingId=1&limit=10)
GET {{host}}/api/sync/logs?limit=10
Cookie: user_id=dev-user-1


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Webhook (simulate Spotify sending a change notification)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Spotify webhook challenge handshake
POST {{host}}/api/sync/webhook/spotify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "challenge": "test-challenge-abc123",
  "items": null
}

###

### Simulate Spotify playlist change event (replace playlist ID)
POST {{host}}/api/sync/webhook/spotify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "challenge": null,
  "items": [
    { "uri": "spotify:playlist:37i9dQZF1DXcBWIGoYBM5M", "type": "playlist" }
  ]
}
